{"tid":1380991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"730港鐵不合作要人多先會成功！","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:45:04.000Z","uid":263944,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75ab9a14405871b49aa5bd78c273ffdeaf90fa9c","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"次次有遊行，港鐵都會塞爆。<br />\n卡門，撳制，都只係阻到下，但係如果地鐵塞爆晒人，你淨係企出黎，港鐵都會癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n如果你：<br />\n忍夠不負責任既政府，<br />\n心痛元朗事件被人打到出晒血，<br />\n睇唔過警察違反人權既暴力，<br />\n不能接受縱容黑社會嘅制度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你要企出黎！</span><br />\n只要你係調景嶺線不斷咁loop，<br />\n做到係港鐵入面遊行，港鐵就會癱瘓。<br />\n唔洗一定要著黑衫，扮係普通市民搭港鐵，<br />\n就可以減低手足既群眾壓力。<br />\n<br />\n琴日嘅手足打生打死，我哋唔係早啲起身去港鐵歎吓冷氣都唔敢阿？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xN8TPSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxN8TPSf.jpg&h=f5ee382b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"651ed3d3cde9ad6fe8ece66f0dad4d6dcf0f3350","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全城罷工！"},{"pid":"7753b7bf441222ec7af34a4de3c84774e9cf6a6a","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全城罷工！"},{"pid":"2dac5bfe9052072a34743de453be4f3c629ab9fc","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全城罷工！"},{"pid":"4d3694a198300a5782436de293898c05c3d6f09f","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全城罷工！"},{"pid":"8c1eb090d59999da19e0d528dfcffa32b71b8f27","tid":1380991,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"7ffb7285a0c92fbaedbd7bab01c92221c7f884f2","tid":1380991,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全城罷工！"},{"pid":"d9dde